efis_to_hud $ hud.cfg (Look at HUD.cfg file)
-------------------------------
[HUD]
#when running in xwindows,mac,win this will show hud in window if set.
#window=640,480
# define the drawable area for hud to use.  Useful on displays that have hidden areas.
# this is defined as x1,y1,x2,y2 to draw up a box of usable area.
drawable_area=0,159,1280,651

[Formats]
speed_distance = Knots
temperature = F
------------------------------
Run Commands
Data Saving while Running
Start = Ctrl-W
Stop = Ctrl-E

Debug while running
Ctrl-D (Start & Stop)

Change from HUD Graphics to Data Text mode
Ctrl=t

